# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s14_324ab337:

    # "We ended up spending the night in a department store parking lot. There were plenty of rest stops, but those are off the table—permanently."
    "Terminamos pasando la noche en el estacionamiento de una tienda departamental. Había muchas áreas de descanso, pero esas están descartadas—para siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s14_709de01c:

    # "Like usual, I woke up pretty early and got us on the road again. Even after waking up briefly, Marina passed back out until we were already in Moab."
    "Como de costumbre, me desperté bastante temprano y nos puse de nuevo en camino. Incluso después de despertarse brevemente, Marina volvió a dormirse hasta que ya estábamos en Moab."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s14_f59cf930:

    # "Moab’s the quintessential \"outdoorsy\" town. It’s built alongside the Colorado River, winding through a canyon. Every other store sells rafting supplies or hiking gear or camping equipment."
    "Moab es el pueblo \"aventurero\" por excelencia. Está construido a lo largo del río Colorado, serpenteando por un cañón. Cada dos tiendas venden equipo de rafting, senderismo o campamento."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s14_96f1bbe0:

    # "Even some of the houses are made to look like log cabins and other rustic architecture."
    "Incluso algunas casas están hechas para parecer cabañas de troncos y otra arquitectura rústica."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s14_967e1871:

    # "You can see tall, forested mountains from any part of town, but it’s not entirely out of the desert, either."
    "Desde cualquier parte del pueblo se ven montañas altas y boscosas, pero tampoco está completamente fuera del desierto."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s14_b50dbd1e:

    # "It’s the time of morning where most people are on their way to work. There’s a disgustingly large amount of traffic."
    "Es la hora de la mañana en que la mayoría de la gente va al trabajo. Hay una cantidad asquerosamente grande de tráfico."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s14_6010c79c:

    # "It’s obvious why. Shovels and pickaxes stick out of truck beds and cracked windows like porcupine quills."
    "Es obvio por qué. Palas y picos sobresalen de las camionetas y ventanas rotas como púas de puercoespín."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s14_938b8522:

    # "At a glance, I’d say three quarters of the people contributing to our glacial pace are prospectors. Which means I don’t have any room to complain."
    "De un vistazo, diría que tres cuartas partes de la gente que contribuye a nuestro paso glacial son buscadores de tesoros. Lo que significa que no tengo derecho a quejarme."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s14_2dad2f8a:

    # "After watching the next light change three times, but still not reaching it myself, I sigh and pull into a nearby diner."
    "Después de ver el siguiente semáforo cambiar tres veces, pero sin llegar a él todavía, suspiro y me desvío hacia una cafetería cercana."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s14_67189786:

    # "At first I was just planning to grab some coffee and a bagel, and something for when Marina wakes up."
    "Al principio solo planeaba comprar un café y un bagel, y algo para cuando Marina se despertara."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s14_0fa42f93:

    # "But with her trademark perfect timing, I hear her climb out of bed right as I turn off the RV."
    "Pero con su característico timing perfecto, la oigo levantarse de la cama justo cuando apago la RV."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s14_36ca7648:

    # Marina "We there? Is this Arches?"
    Marina "Мы уже на месте? Это парк Арчес?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s14_837d4156:

    # "She stumbles up to the front still looking mostly asleep. I don’t know how she can still be tired—she must have gotten 10 hours."
    "Se tambalea hacia el frente todavía medio dormida. No sé cómo puede seguir cansada—debe haber dormido 10 horas."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s14_c2a44b70:

    # Amber "Close. We're in Moab. Arches is still a few miles up the road."
    Amber "Почти. Мы в Моабе. Арчес в нескольких милях отсюда."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s14_618f2c0c:

    # Marina "Oh. Why'd we stop?"
    Marina "О. А почему мы остановились?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s14_b513aed3:

    # Amber "'Cause I’m hungry. And traffic’s practically stalled. It could be lunch time before we get there."
    Amber "Потому что я голодна. И движение транспорта практически остановилось. Так мы доберемся туда не раньше обеда."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:130
translate spanish hwb_s14_5f0c1b33:

    # Marina "You were just gonna eat without me?"
    Marina "И ты собиралась идти кушать без меня?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:132
translate spanish hwb_s14_1b2aa36b:

    # "Even through her grogginess, she sounds shocked and offended."
    "Incluso entre su somnolencia, suena sorprendida y ofendida."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:136
translate spanish hwb_s14_61c4e9b1:

    # Amber "I was gonna grab you something to go. But I will eat without you if you don’t get ready fast."
    Amber "Я собиралась взять тебе что-то с собой. Но я пойду есть без тебя, если ты мигом не соберешься."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s14_9c0fb36d:

    # Marina "Meanie."
    Marina "Злюка."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s14_2b8e8002:

    # Amber "Yeah, yeah. Complain about me once you're dressed."
    Amber "Да, да. Можешь жаловаться на меня после того как оденешься."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s14_b2c13312:

    # "I can see the start of a smile as she turns back to get ready. I inspect my nails while I wait."
    "Veo el inicio de una sonrisa cuando se da la vuelta para alistarse. Me reviso las uñas mientras espero."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s14_904e72bc:

    # "A few minutes later and she hops up front like the Easter Bunny, chipper as ever."
    "Unos minutos después, salta al frente como el Conejo de Pascua, más alegre que nunca."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s14_2484290c:

    # Amber "It’s like your energy is stored in your outfit or something. You get dressed and wake right up."
    Amber "Такое ощущение, что вся твоя энергия заключена в твоей одежде. Ты оделась и сразу же взбодрилась."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s14_8f2548e5:

    # "Marina puts on airs."
    "Marina se da aires."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s14_f8867b2e:

    # Marina "I don’t know what you mean. I’m always cheerful and alert."
    Marina "Не знаю о чем ты. Я всегда жизнерадостна и готова ко всему."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s14_3f20face:

    # Amber "Uh huh. Did you know that you snore?"
    Amber "Ага. А ты в курсе, что храпишь?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s14_360589ec:

    # "Her pretense is dropped in a flash."
    "Su farsa se desvanece en un instante."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s14_dd98ba0d:

    # Marina "Do not!"
    Marina "Не храплю!"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s14_ad5fe245:

    # Amber "You do."
    Amber "Храпишь."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:187
translate spanish hwb_s14_47820500:

    # "I lead the way out of the RV."
    "Guío el camino fuera de la RV."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s14_9665b338:

    # Amber "Loud. Like an elephant seal."
    Amber "Громко. Как морской слон."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s14_163a09b3:

    # "Marina blusters about for a retort while I just wait by the door, laughing."
    "Marina busca una réplica mientras yo solo espero junto a la puerta, riendo."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s14_32627013:

    # "She makes a \"hmph\" noise as she passes by me, crossing the parking lot. Still, she holds the door for me as we go into the diner."
    "Hace un sonido de \"hmph\" al pasar a mi lado, cruzando el estacionamiento. Aun así, me sostiene la puerta al entrar a la cafetería."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s14_dc1b8573:

    # "There’s a \"Seat yourself!\" sign up near the front, along with a stack of menus. I grab two off the top."
    "Hay un letrero de \"Siéntese usted mismo\" cerca de la entrada, junto con una pila de menús. Tomo dos de arriba."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s14_18992a3a:

    # Amber "Do you need a kid's menu? With the crayons?"
    Amber "Тебе прихватить детское меню и мелки?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s14_8dfaae22:

    # "I’m just teasing her more, but her face lights up."
    "Solo la estoy molestando más, pero su rostro se ilumina."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s14_eb7001c4:

    # Marina "Ooh, they have those? Yeah, gimme one!"
    Marina "Ооо, а у них и такое есть? Да, да, прихвати мне!"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s14_a450a56b:

    # "Mentally facepalming, I also take a coloring sheet and cup of crayons."
    "Mentalmente me doy una palmada en la frente, también tomo una hoja para colorear y un vaso de crayones."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s14_14699ee2:

    # "We find a booth by the window near the middle of the restaurant, between a family of four and a couple around our age. It might be the only empty spot in the whole place."
    "Encontramos una cabina junto a la ventana en medio del restaurante, entre una familia de cuatro y una pareja de nuestra edad. Podría ser el único lugar vacío en todo el sitio."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s14_98c77567:

    # "While I look over the breakfast specials, Marina eagerly begins to color. She’s got a dark green, two shades of red, a blue, and a yellow crayon."
    "Mientras reviso los especiales de desayuno, Marina comienza a colorear con entusiasmo. Tiene un crayón verde oscuro, dos tonos de rojo, uno azul y uno amarillo."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s14_2613a462:

    # "Of course, they’re worn down to being practically round on the bottoms, which makes it hard for her to stay inside the lines."
    "Claro, están tan desgastadas que las puntas son prácticamente redondas, lo que le dificulta mantenerse dentro de las líneas."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s14_cfc6faf1:

    # "When I shift my legs, I accidentally bump the table with my foot and cause her to make a large green streak across the personified eggs she was coloring."
    "Cuando muevo las piernas, sin querer golpeo la mesa con el pie y hago que ella trace una gran raya verde sobre los huevos personificados que estaba coloreando."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s14_f118d031:

    # Amber "Oops, sorry."
    Amber "Упс, извини."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s14_f084b8bd:

    # Marina "It’s okay. What is it they say? 'There are no mistakes in art, just happy accidents?'"
    Marina "Да ладно. Как там говорят? “В искусстве нет ошибок, есть только счастливые случайности”?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s14_226084ea:

    # Amber "Something like that."
    Amber "Что-то вроде того."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s14_b1dbc1c4:

    # Amber "Why green?"
    Amber "Почему зеленый цвет?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s14_a263a0f7:

    # Marina "Do you not see what I’m coloring here, Sam-I-Amber?"
    Marina "Ты что, не видишь, что я тут раскрашиваю, “Вот-так-Сэмбер”?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s14_76310530:

    # Marina "Plus, this is clearly a Phthalo Green that I'm going to be later coupling with a Van Dyke Brown."
    Marina "К тому же это однозначно Фтало-Зеленый, который я затем смешаю с Ван-Дик-Коричневым."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s14_eddb8060:

    # Marina "These are going to be the happiest accidents you've ever seen."
    Marina "Это будут самые счастливые случайности, которые ты когда-либо видела."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s14_fbe0cea4:

    # "I groan aloud at her awful joke. I’m saved from more of them by the arrival of the same waitress who greeted us. Her white uniform is stained with jelly and ketchup and who knows what else."
    "Gimo en voz alta por su pésimo chiste. Me salva de más de ellos la llegada de la misma mesera que nos recibió. Su uniforme blanco está manchado de jalea, kétchup y quién sabe qué más."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s14_04e22976:

    # Waitress "Can I get you girls something to drink?"
    Waitress "Девочки, могу я принести вам что-нибудь попить?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s14_ebb981b4:

    # Marina "I’ll have some chocolate milk, please!"
    Marina "Мне шоколадного молочка, пожалуйста!"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s14_2d808d42:

    # "Her already questionable maturity suffers another blow. With the crayons in her hand, I’m not sure it can stand to take any more hits."
    "Su ya cuestionable madurez recibe otro golpe. Con los crayones en la mano, no estoy segura de que pueda soportar más."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s14_b0041337:

    # Waitress "And for you?"
    Waitress "А вам?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s14_ef10036f:

    # Amber "Just coffee. No cream or sugar."
    Amber "Просто кофе. Без сливок и сахара."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s14_cb15232e:

    # Waitress "You got it."
    Waitress "Хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s14_68163960:

    # "Once she walks away, I nudge Marina with my foot."
    "Una vez que se aleja, empujo a Marina con el pie."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s14_282da605:

    # Amber "Chocolate milk? Seriously? Are you eight?"
    Amber "Шоколадное молоко? Серьезно? Тебе что, восемь лет?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s14_4a6b60fd:

    # "Mimicking my voice, Marina shakes her shoulders."
    "Imitando mi voz, Marina sacude los hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s14_d17f2269:

    # Marina "Black coffee? Seriously? Are you forty?"
    Marina "Черный кофе? Серьезно? Тебе что, сорок лет?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s14_9b98940e:

    # Amber "Hey now, I like the taste of coffee itself."
    Amber "Эй, мне нравится сам вкус кофе."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s14_11944634:

    # Marina "And I like the taste of milk itself! Just with chocolate."
    Marina "А мне нравится вкус молока! Только с шоколадом."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s14_87057c31:

    # Amber "You’re a dork."
    Amber "Ну ты и зануда."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s14_d42b8601:

    # Marina "But you love me~"
    Marina "Потому то ты меня и любишь~"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s14_b37921a4:

    # "She chimes back in a singsong voice. I know what she means, but it still causes a small lump to form in my throat. I swallow, trying to pretend that she didn’t hit a little too close to home."
    "Responde con voz cantarina. Sé lo que quiere decir, pero aun así se me forma un pequeño nudo en la garganta. Trago saliva, tratando de fingir que no dio justo en el punto sensible."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s14_e5315f50:

    # "I watch her while she goes back to coloring human/breakfast hybrids. Her lips are pursed in concentration, and there’s a little gleam of white as she bites the edge of one."
    "La observo mientras vuelve a colorear híbridos de humano y desayuno. Tiene los labios fruncidos en concentración, y se ve un pequeño destello blanco mientras muerde el borde de uno."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s14_9f566419:

    # "Seems she’s really focused. Surprisingly, she mostly manages to stay inside the lines of the pictures."
    "Parece que está muy concentrada. Sorprendentemente, logra mantenerse dentro de las líneas de los dibujos la mayor parte del tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s14_062314da:

    # "Rather than trying to use the dull tips, she’s switched to the flat, round ends, using the edge for more precision. It’s… Kind of working?"
    "En lugar de usar las puntas desafiladas, ha cambiado a los extremos planos y redondos, usando el borde para más precisión. Es... ¿Como que funciona?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s14_94f8937e:

    # "Without looking up, she starts to chat again."
    "Sin levantar la vista, empieza a hablar de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s14_b9e0da00:

    # Marina "So, where do we start looking today, Captain?"
    Marina "Ну, с чего мы начнем поиски сегодня, Капитан?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s14_275dde49:

    # Amber "Oh, you finally acknowledge me as captain then, huh?"
    Amber "О, ты наконец-то признала меня в качестве капитана, а?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:372
translate spanish hwb_s14_44e200d7:

    # Marina "I figured you deserve a turn. Just this once."
    Marina "Я подумала, что ты заслужила что-то хорошее в ответ. Но только в этот раз."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:376
translate spanish hwb_s14_6cd4c6f9:

    # Amber "Thanks. I’ll try not to let you down."
    Amber "Спасибо. Я постараюсь не разочаровать тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:382
translate spanish hwb_s14_58fa3b90:

    # Amber "Anyway, I have no idea."
    Amber "Но в любом случае - я не знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s14_b9e8cf23:

    # Marina "You said you think it’s by one of the arches, right?"
    Marina "Ты сказала, что думаешь, что оно где-то возле одной из арок, так?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:388
translate spanish hwb_s14_45868dc3:

    # Amber "Well yeah. But that doesn’t really narrow it down."
    Amber "Ну да. Но это не особо упрощает задачу."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s14_505fb24a:

    # "Pausing her coloring, she looks up at me."
    "Pausando su coloreado, me mira."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:394
translate spanish hwb_s14_68a2b042:

    # Marina "It doesn’t?"
    Marina "Не упрощает?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s14_b2ed91d9:

    # Amber "Nah. Have you ever seen any pictures of the park?"
    Amber "Неа. Ты когда-нибудь видела картинки парка?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s14_9ce0c56a:

    # Marina "A couple, I guess. I don’t know much about it though."
    Marina "Парочку, вроде бы. Но я не особо что-то о них знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s14_9463543d:

    # Amber "Well, they named the park after the arches since there are so many of them. Probably hundreds."
    Amber "Ну, они назвали парк в честь арок, так как их там очень много. Около сотни."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s14_84b6d8e2:

    # Marina "Seriously?"
    Marina "Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s14_350485d9:

    # Amber "Yeah. Some are more famous than others. Let’s see…"
    Amber "Ага. Некоторые более известные, некоторые - менее. Давай подумаем…"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s14_1f64de19:

    # Amber "There’s Windstone Arch and Double Arch; those are some of the more famous ones. You’ve probably seen pictures of those, even if you don’t know it."
    Amber "Там есть арка “Уиндстоун”, “Двойная” арка - это из известных. Ты точно видела их изображения, даже если и сама не догадываешься об этом."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s14_10506d4b:

    # Amber "But there are a ton of lesser known ones, too. And for all we know, the treasure could be at one of them that doesn’t even have a name."
    Amber "Но там так же куча менее известных. И, в общем-то, сокровище может находиться под той, у которой вообще нет своего названия."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s14_4b9e8b3a:

    # Marina "So we’re screwed."
    Marina "То есть мы облажались."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s14_1036d24d:

    # Amber "Probably. But that doesn’t mean we’re giving up."
    Amber "Возможно. Но это не значит, что мы сдаемся."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s14_cfed54fb:

    # "Marina nods in satisfaction, either at my words or the slice of blue ham she just finished coloring."
    "Marina asiente con satisfacción, ya sea por mis palabras o por la rebanada de jamón azul que acaba de colorear."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s14_7b56584c:

    # Amber "I don’t wanna lose twice in a row. So I figure we’ll go and look around, and see if there are any clues."
    Amber "Я не хочу проиграть два раза подряд. Так что я думаю, мы там осмотримся и поищем, нет ли каких-либо зацепок."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s14_88fb54f5:

    # Amber "Maybe watch what other people are doing and thinking."
    Amber "Может быть взглянем, что там делают и в каком направлении мыслят другие люди."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s14_d1e8f783:

    # "Marina nods along, but she has a zoned-out look that tells me she’s not really listening. Rather, she seems to be staring past me."
    "Marina asiente, pero tiene una mirada ausente que me dice que no está escuchando realmente. Más bien, parece estar mirando más allá de mí."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s14_de3c155e:

    # "I turn, trying to figure out what might be attracting her attention. There’s nothing except for other groups eating. I make awkward eye contact with the old lady right beside us, and I quickly face forward."
    "Me giro, tratando de averiguar qué podría estar atrayendo su atención. No hay nada excepto otros grupos comiendo. Hago un incómodo contacto visual con la anciana justo a nuestro lado, y rápidamente vuelvo a mirar al frente."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s14_ace5fdc0:

    # Amber "Inspecting the walls?"
    Amber "Изучаешь стену?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s14_23b9e5f4:

    # "My words seem to break the spell."
    "Mis palabras parecen romper el hechizo."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s14_71e617a8:

    # Marina "{cps=8}H-{w=0.3}{cps=80}huh?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=8}Х-{w=0.3}{cps=80}Хм?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s14_32827167:

    # Amber "You totally spaced out there."
    Amber "Ты в совершенной прострации."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s14_a5a4cf88:

    # Marina "Oops, yeah. Sorry, I just started thinking."
    Marina "Упс, да. Прости, я тут начала думать."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s14_9d220c5a:

    # "Before I can ask her what about, our waitress returns."
    "Antes de que pueda preguntarle qué pasa, nuestra mesera regresa."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s14_cf748bf3:

    # "Our drinks are balanced on a tray alongside a few other guests’. Marina’s chocolate milk comes in an enormous tin cup that’s the size of my forearm. And there’s an entire pot of coffee for me."
    "Nuestras bebidas están equilibradas en una bandeja junto con las de otros clientes. La leche con chocolate de Marina viene en una taza de hojalata enorme del tamaño de mi antebrazo. Y hay una jarra entera de café para mí."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s14_16458ea4:

    # "She sets them down on the table between us."
    "Las coloca en la mesa entre nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s14_ff58befd:

    # Waitress "You girls ready to order?"
    Waitress "Девочки, вы готовы сделать заказ?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s14_0e366b44:

    # "Whoops. I haven’t looked through the menu once. I flip through it real quick, settling on a standard meal."
    "Vaya. No he mirado el menú ni una vez. Lo hojeo rápido y decido un plato estándar."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s14_d8e6dd94:

    # Amber "You good?"
    Amber "Тебя устраивает?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:472
translate spanish hwb_s14_8cca6a15:

    # "Marina nods."
    "Marina asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:476
translate spanish hwb_s14_f46b243c:

    # Amber "I’ll have the Gentleman’s Breakfast with bacon. Eggs over-medium and sourdough toast."
    Amber "Мне “Джентльменский завтрак с беконом”. Яйца чуть выше средней прожарки и дрожжевой тост."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s14_b0041337_1:

    # Waitress "And for you?"
    Waitress "А вам?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s14_6f1f31f4:

    # Marina "Um, {w=0.5}I’ll have the chocolate chip pancake platter with scrambled eggs."
    Marina "Эм, {w=0.5}мне блинчики с шоколадом и омлет."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:486
translate spanish hwb_s14_dd80eb8d:

    # Waitress "You want the kids meal or the regular?"
    Waitress "Детский размер или обычный?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:492
translate spanish hwb_s14_b8b05c1c:

    # "I choke on my drink as I laugh, and feel Marina’s foot crash against my leg. Whimpering at that and the dribble of coffee on my chin, I massage my shin underneath the table."
    "Me atraganto con mi bebida mientras me río, y siento el pie de Marina chocar contra mi pierna. Gimoteando por eso y por el chorrito de café en mi barbilla, me masajeo la espinilla debajo de la mesa."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:496
translate spanish hwb_s14_43480301:

    # "Marina frowns at me, and the waitress gives me a strange look. Then the typical angelic expression returns as Marina places her order."
    "Marina frunce el ceño hacia mí, y la mesera me da una mirada extraña. Luego, la típica expresión angelical regresa mientras Marina hace su pedido."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:500
translate spanish hwb_s14_016372ed:

    # Marina "The regular, please and thanks."
    Marina "Обычный, пожалуйста. Спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:502
translate spanish hwb_s14_904703c9:

    # Waitress "We’ll have that out for you pretty soon."
    Waitress "Скоро будет готово."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s14_20920949:

    # "Once again, she heads back to the kitchen, heels clicking against the tile floor."
    "Una vez más, se dirige a la cocina, con los tacones haciendo clic contra el piso de baldosas."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:508
translate spanish hwb_s14_6b93a3df:

    # "When she’s out of sight, Marina begins a flurry of kicks to my shins, though these ones aren’t hard enough to hurt. Scurrying backwards in my seat, I draw my legs up closer to me."
    "Cuando desaparece de la vista, Marina comienza una ráfaga de patadas en mis espinillas, aunque estas no son lo suficientemente fuertes como para doler. Retrocediendo en mi asiento, acerco las piernas hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:510
translate spanish hwb_s14_8d951f05:

    # Marina "Rude! Rude, rude, rude!"
    Marina "Грубо! Грубо, грубо, грууубоооо!"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:514
translate spanish hwb_s14_05351f9d:

    # Amber "C’mon, you were asking for it with the food and the milk. The waitress asking that was just icing on the cake. The pancake."
    Amber "Да ладно, ты сама напрашивалась на это своим выбором еды и шоколадным молоком. Официантка просто спросила о том, что было бы на поверхности блинчиков."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:516
translate spanish hwb_s14_f80918e6:

    # Marina "It’s not my fault that you {i}sophisticated{/i} adults don’t appreciate chocolate like I do."
    Marina "Это не моя вина, что вы, {i}утонченные{/i} взрослые, не цените шоколад так, как ценю его я."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:520
translate spanish hwb_s14_443fc1c1:

    # Amber "You have a bigger sweet tooth than anyone I’ve ever met. Seriously, how many cavities have you had?"
    Amber "У тебя самый заточенный на сладкое зуб из всех, кого я встречала. Серьезно, как обстоят дела у твоих зубов с кариесом?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:524
translate spanish hwb_s14_f4a615cd:

    # Marina "None~ I brush my teeth twice a day, every day. The last time I went to the dentist, he said my teeth were so shiny he could see his reflection in them."
    Marina "Никак~ я чищу зубы дважды в день. Каждый день. Когда последний раз я была у дантиста, он сказал, что мои зубы настолько блестящие, что он видит в них свое отражение."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s14_cf7fe254:

    # Amber "And when was that?"
    Amber "И когда же это было?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:530
translate spanish hwb_s14_7cc40ad9:

    # "She thinks about it for a minute."
    "Lo piensa por un minuto."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:534
translate spanish hwb_s14_d3b48058:

    # Marina "Maybe three years?"
    Marina "Может года три назад."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:538
translate spanish hwb_s14_49df90bd:

    # Amber "That doesn’t count anymore then."
    Amber "Тогда это уже не считается."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:542
translate spanish hwb_s14_b5630ccf:

    # Marina "When was the last time that {i}you{/i} had chocolate milk?"
    Marina "А когда был последний раз, когда {i}ты{/i} пила шоколадное молоко?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:544
translate spanish hwb_s14_f88518f8:

    # "Now I have to think about that. I don’t drink a whole lot of milk to begin with, and as for chocolate…"
    "Ahora tengo que pensar en eso. De por sí no tomo mucha leche, y en cuanto al chocolate..."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:548
translate spanish hwb_s14_7a2b5c4c:

    # Amber "Um, maybe when I was a little kid? I don’t know."
    Amber "Эм, может когда я была ребенком? Понятия не имею."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:552
translate spanish hwb_s14_71b688dc:

    # Marina "Amber. {w=0.8}Amber, you poor, poor thing."
    Marina "Эмбер. {w=0.8}Эмбер, ты бедная, бедная бедняжка."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:554
translate spanish hwb_s14_77bf46cb:

    # "She slides her giant cup towards me, some sloshing over the sides in her haste."
    "Desliza su taza gigante hacia mí, derramando un poco por los lados en su apuro."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:558
translate spanish hwb_s14_332258c2:

    # Marina "Try it."
    Marina "Пробуй."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:562
translate spanish hwb_s14_96b551de:

    # "Dredges of milk surround the rim of the cup from Marina’s sipping. Across from me, she waits, looking eager. I’m surprised she’s not bouncing like normal."
    "Restos de leche rodean el borde de la taza por los sorbos de Marina. Frente a mí, ella espera, con aspecto ansioso. Me sorprende que no esté saltando como siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s14_ecd1c10c:

    # "After sighing exaggeratedly, I pick up the cup and down a large gulp, trying not to think silly, cliche thoughts about \"indirect kisses.\""
    "Tras suspirar de forma exagerada, tomo la taza y doy un gran trago, tratando de no pensar en tonterías cliché sobre \"besos indirectos\"."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:570
translate spanish hwb_s14_ecdbc0df:

    # "To my surprise, the drink is… Really good."
    "Para mi sorpresa, la bebida es... realmente buena."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:572
translate spanish hwb_s14_3b73e540:

    # "It’s got a deeper, rich flavor than the stuff you get in jugs at the store. I can tell that they made it themselves in the kitchen."
    "Tiene un sabor más profundo y rico que el que compras en jarras en la tienda. Puedo notar que lo hicieron ellos mismos en la cocina."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:576
translate spanish hwb_s14_4b338ee2:

    # "It’s not overwhelmingly sweet. In fact, it’s perfect."
    "No es excesivamente dulce. De hecho, es perfecto."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:578
translate spanish hwb_s14_7f0e2737:

    # "Damn. I don’t know if I’m disappointed or not. Giving her the satisfaction of being right..."
    "Maldición. No sé si estoy decepcionada o no. Darle la satisfacción de tener razón..."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:580
translate spanish hwb_s14_ff7bdfef:

    # "My pride aches."
    "Mi orgullo duele."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:584
translate spanish hwb_s14_3e3928f8:

    # "As I push the cup back towards Marina, she receives it with a sly smirk."
    "Al devolverle la taza a Marina, ella la recibe con una sonrisa burlona."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:586
translate spanish hwb_s14_67bc9dc8:

    # Marina "{cps=5}Soooo?{/cps}"
    Marina "{cps=5}Нууу иии?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:588
translate spanish hwb_s14_3c587230:

    # "She draws out the word, already knowing my answer."
    "Alarga la palabra, ya sabiendo mi respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:592
translate spanish hwb_s14_a1691827:

    # Amber "It wasn’t bad."
    Amber "Не так уж и плохо."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:594
translate spanish hwb_s14_90e00a92:

    # "That’s all I’m willing to concede."
    "Eso es todo lo que estoy dispuesta a conceder."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:598
translate spanish hwb_s14_8307d353:

    # "She laughs and takes another huge sip. After setting the cup down, she has a thick milk mustache on her upper lip. I watch with inappropriate fascination as her tongue comes out and cleans it away."
    "Se ríe y da otro enorme sorbo. Al dejar la taza, tiene un bigote de leche espeso en el labio superior. Miro con fascinación inapropiada mientras su lengua sale y lo limpia."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:602
translate spanish hwb_s14_948063fa:

    # "Marina grabs the sheet she was coloring and then pushes that over to me as well."
    "Marina agarra la hoja que estaba coloreando y luego la empuja hacia mí también."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:604
translate spanish hwb_s14_58db2e56:

    # Marina "Wanna color something?"
    Marina "Хочешь раскрасить что-нибудь?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:606
translate spanish hwb_s14_90d04f99:

    # Marina "While you’re acting like a kid and all."
    Marina "Ну, пока ты еще ведешь себя как ребенок и все такое."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:610
translate spanish hwb_s14_6046fe55:

    # "I roll my eyes but snatch away the crayons that she offers."
    "Pongo los ojos en blanco, pero arrebato los crayones que me ofrece."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:614
translate spanish hwb_s14_26f6256a:

    # "Most of the pictures - all of them breakfast foods with faces and dated outfits - have already been colored in."
    "La mayoría de los dibujos —todos alimentos del desayuno con caras y atuendos pasados de moda— ya están coloreados."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:616
translate spanish hwb_s14_d20fc801:

    # "There’s a stylish looking piece of bread with a dress and a wig that’s still blank, though. I color the dress with the green crayon as lightly as I can, and use the lighter shade of red for the hair."
    "Sin embargo, hay un pan con estilo, con un vestido y una peluca, que aún está en blanco. Coloreo el vestido con el crayón verde lo más suave que puedo, y uso el tono más claro de rojo para el cabello."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:620
translate spanish hwb_s14_2d38fc5c:

    # "When I’m done, I hold up the page to show Marina."
    "Cuando termino, levanto la página para mostrársela a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:622
translate spanish hwb_s14_73915d4b:

    # Amber "It’s you."
    Amber "Это ты."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:626
translate spanish hwb_s14_99604f73:

    # "She leans in."
    "Se inclina."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:628
translate spanish hwb_s14_5b48006b:

    # Marina "Huh?"
    Marina "Эм?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:632
translate spanish hwb_s14_4f575871:

    # Amber "The colors. Look, you’re toast."
    Amber "Цвета. Смотри, ты тост."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:636
translate spanish hwb_s14_cc7711bf:

    # "She collapses backwards as if my pun physically wounded her. She shakes her head and looks down while I crack up."
    "Se desploma hacia atrás como si mi juego de palabras la hubiera herido físicamente. Niega con la cabeza y mira hacia abajo mientras yo me parto de risa."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:638
translate spanish hwb_s14_199479fc:

    # Marina "That was even worse than ‘Sam-I-Amber.’"
    Marina "Это даже хуже, чем мой вариант с “Вот-так-Сэмбер”."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:642
translate spanish hwb_s14_ca6feb29:

    # Amber "Uh huh. You butter step your game up some."
    Amber "Ага. Ты сама вывела эту игру на этот скользкий путь."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s14_a9f8dda6:

    # Marina "Please stop."
    Marina "Пожалуйста, прекрати."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:648
translate spanish hwb_s14_f1d58e40:

    # "I don’t plan to. The only thing that saves her is the arrival of our waitress right then."
    "No pienso hacerlo. Lo único que la salva es la llegada de nuestra mesera justo en ese momento."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:650
translate spanish hwb_s14_a74bb993:

    # "That’s pretty fast service, considering how busy this place is."
    "Es un servicio bastante rápido, considerando lo lleno que está este lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:654
translate spanish hwb_s14_15ea201e:

    # "Keeping in style with our oversized beverages, the portions are enormous."
    "Siguiendo el estilo de nuestras bebidas gigantes, las porciones son enormes."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s14_5f62c2de:

    # "The plate that Marina’s pancakes are served on is so large, it looks like it could’ve been used as a shield back in medieval times. And the pancakes form a tower that’s probably half a foot tall."
    "El plato en el que sirven los panqueques de Marina es tan grande que parece que podría haber sido usado como escudo en la época medieval. Y los panqueques forman una torre que probablemente mide medio pie de alto."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:660
translate spanish hwb_s14_fe354b25:

    # "My own meal arrives on four separate plates, though they’re all smaller than Marina’s. We have to scramble and move our drinks around just to make room. There’s hardly any empty space."
    "Mi propia comida llega en cuatro platos separados, aunque todos son más pequeños que el de Marina. Tenemos que apresurarnos y mover nuestras bebidas solo para hacer espacio. Casi no queda espacio vacío."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:662
translate spanish hwb_s14_7cd2bfe8:

    # Waitress "Can I get you girls anything else?"
    Waitress "Что-нибудь еще, девочки?"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:666
translate spanish hwb_s14_5126630d:

    # "Marina shakes her head, but I look down at the table as I mumble:"
    "Marina niega con la cabeza, pero yo miro hacia abajo a la mesa mientras murmuro:"

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:670
translate spanish hwb_s14_30a35498:

    # Amber "Can I get a glass of chocolate milk, please?"
    Amber "Стакан шоколадного молока, пожалуйста."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:672
translate spanish hwb_s14_19488ecf:

    # "As the waitress departs yet again, I glance over, prepared for the inevitable teasing. But instead, Marina just stares at her food, dumbstruck."
    "Mientras la mesera se va de nuevo, miro de reojo, preparada para las inevitables burlas. Pero en cambio, Marina solo se queda mirando su comida, atónita."

# game/script/hwb_s14.rpy:678
translate spanish hwb_s14_7eb1e8bf:

    # Marina "{cps=3}...{cps=80}Maybe I should've gotten the kids' size."
    Marina "{cps=3}...{cps=80}Может мне все же стоило выбрать детскую порцию."

